{"tid":510539,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【3千觀眾送驚喜】渡邊麻友臨別AKB 收祝福喊唔出","createTime":"2017-12-26T14:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T03:48:19.000Z","uid":3806,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"76dfed5e0ffdd7f7c1a8ca5c2db6e4f4bce73a8a","tid":510539,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T14:59:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171222/large/1513950334_6d51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171222%2Flarge%2F1513950334_6d51.jpg&h=b6a9b298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朝日電視台噚晚直播四小時節目《Music Station Super Live》，邀得不同年代樂壇紅人輪流表演，當中包括X JAPAN、LUNA SEA、福山雅治、平井堅、柚子、KinKi Kids、嵐、金爆、椎名林檎、西野加奈、AI、荻野目洋子、倉木麻衣、乃木坂46、櫸坂46、AKB48等，仲有於日本人集急升嘅K-POP偶像TWICE及BTS，場面熱鬧。<br />\n<br />\nAKB「二奶」渡邊麻友即將離隊，佢今次肯定係最後一次以AKB成員身份亮相《Music Station Super Live》，當佢帶領隊友大熱AKB名曲之際，唱至單曲《心意告示牌》，全場3千觀眾竟齊齊舉起寫上祝福麻友嘅心意卡，為佢送上驚喜，令麻友顯得一臉愕然，更被大會攝影機多次大特寫，可惜麻友都係咇唔出眼淚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171222/large/1513950336_e2d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171222%2Flarge%2F1513950336_e2d4.jpg&h=ae6a11a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171222/large/1513950338_0d9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171222%2Flarge%2F1513950338_0d9a.jpg&h=77b4c1f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好喊呀！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171222/large/1513950339_131b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171222%2Flarge%2F1513950339_131b.jpg&h=0533ff7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSorry....係咇唔出眼淚嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171222/large/1513950356_6289.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171222%2Flarge%2F1513950356_6289.jpg&h=b8974688&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fb8260c5284840f33a6f09e2ee50c76f7d11a66","tid":510539,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T15:00:11.000Z","msg":"𨳒蘋果老母，係我被ban期間出d咁既𨶙屎文侮辱麻友<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f56ef39a40ae44d98f0b9620d878bd53c829da6","tid":510539,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T02:32:15.000Z","msg":"蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491b64cc7c4fe4d4921ebf6de1918b18013f72b1","tid":510539,"uid":43979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:41:56.000Z","msg":"臭g<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0b2062196176b74d7e90ae8f8f8ae047b5e603","tid":510539,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"491b64cc7c4fe4d4921ebf6de1918b18013f72b1","tid":510539,"uid":43979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:41:56.000Z","msg":"臭g<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:43:17.000Z","msg":"太感動，喊乾哂喊唔出"},{"pid":"5220200ed62fab2713da26f625e51a6fbbc87d2c","tid":510539,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:48:19.000Z","msg":"轉行做修女？"}]}